---
---
<section id="features" class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden bg-slate-50/50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
        <div class="text-center mb-16" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black font-display text-[#121417] tracking-tight">Fitur Canggih, Mudah Digunakan</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-base md:text-lg">Dari pencatatan transaksi harian hingga analisis otomatis—semua terkelola dalam satu aplikasi ringan di HP Anda.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- Feature 1 (Flagship: Kelola Stok) -->
            <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100" class="lg:col-span-2 p-8 md:p-10 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#1f5aa2]/40 transition-all duration-300 group relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center justify-between gap-6">
                <div class="relative z-10 max-w-lg">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#1f5aa2]/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#1f5aa2] mb-6 font-bold shadow-sm">
                        <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-[#1f5aa2] bg-[#1f5aa2]/10 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md mb-3 inline-block">Utama</span>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold font-display text-slate-900 mb-3">Kelola Stok & Opname Mudah</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">Catat transaksi masuk & keluar secara akurat secara realtime. Stock opname jadi lebih presisi dan praktis, menghilangkan selisih stok yang sering merugikan bisnis.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="w-full md:w-48 h-36 bg-slate-100 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200/80 flex items-center justify-center p-4 text-slate-400 group-hover:border-[#1f5aa2]/30 transition">
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-boxes-stacked text-3xl text-[#1f5aa2] mb-2"></i>
                        <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700">Realtime Inventory</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 2 (Rekomendasi Stok) -->
            <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200" class="p-8 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#1f5aa2]/40 transition-all duration-300 group relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#1f5aa2]/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#1f5aa2] mb-6 shadow-sm">
                        <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-display text-slate-900 mb-2">Rekomendasi Restock Otomatis</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Sistem menganalisis tren penjualan harian toko Anda dan memberikan peringatan barang yang harus segera di-restock agar jualan tetap lancar.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 3 -->
            <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300" class="p-8 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#1f5aa2]/40 transition-all duration-300 group relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#1f5aa2]/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#1f5aa2] mb-6 shadow-sm">
                        <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-display text-slate-900 mb-2">Analisis & Laporan Ringkas</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Asisten bisnis digital yang siap menjawab pertanyaan seputar omzet dan performa toko Anda secara instan layaknya konsultan pribadi.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 4 -->
            <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400" class="p-8 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#1f5aa2]/40 transition-all duration-300 group relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#1f5aa2]/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#1f5aa2] mb-6 shadow-sm">
                        <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 18h.01M8 21h8a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-display text-slate-900 mb-2">Aplikasi Ringan (Tanpa Install)</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Dapat diakses langsung melalui browser HP atau laptop. Ringan, responsif, dan hemat memori penyimpanan.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 5 -->
            <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100" class="p-8 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#1f5aa2]/40 transition-all duration-300 group relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#1f5aa2]/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#1f5aa2] mb-6 shadow-sm">
                        <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17 17h2a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2h2m2 4h6a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2zm8-12V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v4h10z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-display text-slate-900 mb-2">Cetak Struk Bluetooth</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Mendukung printer thermal 58mm & 80mm via Bluetooth. Cetak struk belanja pelanggan langsung dari smartphone.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 6 (Multi-Kasir) -->
            <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200" class="p-8 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#1f5aa2]/40 transition-all duration-300 group relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#1f5aa2]/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#1f5aa2] mb-6 shadow-sm">
                        <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-display text-slate-900 mb-2">Multi-Kasir & Hak Akses</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Pantau aktivitas transaksi staf Anda secara terpisah. Atur role hak akses kasir & admin secara aman.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 7 (Database Pelanggan & CRM) -->
            <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300" class="p-8 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#1f5aa2]/40 transition-all duration-300 group relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#1f5aa2]/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#1f5aa2] mb-6 shadow-sm">
                        <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-display text-slate-900 mb-2">Database Pelanggan & CRM</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Simpan riwayat belanja pelanggan dan berikan diskon atau loyalty reward khusus untuk tingkatkan pembeli setia toko.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 8 (Pembayaran QRIS & Nontunai) -->
            <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400" class="p-8 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#1f5aa2]/40 transition-all duration-300 group relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#1f5aa2]/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#1f5aa2] mb-6 shadow-sm">
                        <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 10h18M7 15h1m4 0h1m-7 4h12a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-display text-slate-900 mb-2">Pembayaran QRIS & Nontunai</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Terima pembayaran tunai, transfer bank, hingga scan QRIS dengan mudah untuk mempercepat antrean transaksi kasir.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 9 Banner (Laporan Rekapitulasi) Spanning 3 Columns -->
            <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500" class="lg:col-span-3 p-8 bg-[#1f5aa2] rounded-3xl text-white shadow-lg flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
                <div class="max-w-2xl">
                    <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-sky-200 bg-white/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-md mb-3 inline-block">Laporan Rekapitulasi</span>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold font-display text-white mb-2">Laporan Otomatis & Manajemen Diskon</h3>
                    <p class="text-sky-100 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">Dapatkan ringkasan laporan keuangan harian, mingguan, dan bulanan secara otomatis. Atur berbagai skema diskon item atau promo toko dengan praktis.</p>
                </div>
                <a 
                    href="/fitur" 
                    class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3.5 bg-white text-[#1f5aa2] hover:bg-slate-100 active:scale-95 rounded-full font-bold shadow-md transition-all duration-300 flex-shrink-0"
                >
                    <span>Lihat Fitur Lengkap</span> <i class="fas fa-arrow-right text-xs transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1"></i>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


